Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:35.77,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Isabelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:40.41,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm getting used to my new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.18,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:48.31,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sleeping well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.41,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.90,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I was so happy, \NI couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.56,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.37,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.45,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.62,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,How's Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.57,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.42,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.61,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.51,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.93,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell Silver that I don't \Nneed to eat today, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.90,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:54.89,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two weeks since we got back from the \Nchurch, and he still hasn't come out of his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:58.85,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you open the door and ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.99,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:15.49,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the transformation from \Nthe fight took a toll on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.69,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.33,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a lot of energy to \Nchange your appearance, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.12,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that like a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.53,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I can't quite remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:29.54,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it hasn't quite hit \Nme that I'm a fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.58,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you settled in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.31,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been exploring the \Nproperty this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.90,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,It's something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.06,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.35,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,As a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.79,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to admit it, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.33,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.38,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Silky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.77,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:15.20,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know what just happened, \Nbut we got kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.08,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,"For a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.43,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Be back before it gets dark."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.59,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she gave us some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.87,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:33.00,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's safe to \Ngo out right now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.18,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.54,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, long time no see, Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.33,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.33,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.12,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.71,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:52.05,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not asking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.82,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.51,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.61,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a shopping spree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:37.59,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't buy any gifts for Silky, but I'm hoping\N there's something she can use at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.93,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.85,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Now, can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.11,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's functioning properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.85,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.87,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.04,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,She looks sleepy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:54.82,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.08,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You seem especially tired \Nafter you use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:06.02,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to depend on people,\Nor you'll screw something up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.84,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,When you're on your own someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.00,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Chise's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:12.99,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.21,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.01,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to do everything by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:23.39,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, what's the point \Nof having helpful neighbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.62,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You're hot-blooded,\Nbut you have a weak heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.94,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take care of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.36,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.48,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what are \Nyou doing about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:48.00,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You could be going to school, at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.41,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.01,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take care of \Nthe flowers and herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.32,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Studying magic is a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:59.80,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Each season has its own special chores\Nto do and lessons for me to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:06.56,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just content being allowed to \Nstay with Elias and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:11.45,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, are you sure you \Naren't being overly dependent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.28,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.21,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You have a long time ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.20,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spend your time relying\Non handouts from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.73,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,You were bought by Ainsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.63,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,I know you had a hard time elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.56,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't have to be fixed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.99,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.70,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.00,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.41,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.58,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.62,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.22,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.00,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:05.18,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for caring about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.51,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too much of a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Robin, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:23.10,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.43,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm depending on someone who \Ndoesn't think anything of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:33.51,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I tell myself that I wouldn't mind being \Nabandoned, yet I don't want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:39.11,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.81,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I used to hate coming home \Nwhen the lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.07,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.49,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:09:00.06,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I share a little bit of many things with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.34,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.93,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Senses, emotions, and even memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:16.20,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,If that event was a curse put upon\Nyou, I want it to be lifted soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:17.91,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.66,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.32,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.05,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:36.12,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some gifts—I mean, \Nsome snacks and such for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.78,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,How's Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.13,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.98,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.97,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:14.91,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Eli—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.71,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.48,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.26,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control my body very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:29.16,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,It might be scary, but let me stay this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:36.43,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Will you explain things to me in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.19,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.67,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:50.86,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,An inhuman body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.88,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Limbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.67,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.51,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.05,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I'm not scared must be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.76,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.07,Magus-Flashback,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have given birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.08,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.92,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.45,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Silky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.76,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.20,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.64,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, it's time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.51,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Silky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.07,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,Chise-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.52,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.68,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.77,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.15,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.88,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You seem fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.76,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, why did you shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.80,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I can move with you easier in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.49,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.21,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,You must be her familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.62,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good big brother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.23,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.92,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have you seen Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.82,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,Ainsworth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.35,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.73,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.45,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.10,Default,Shovel,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's rubbing off on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.24,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.28,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You must really love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.00,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.26,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of him being gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.35,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,More than that, you're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.27,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.68,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you try to deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.46,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to love \Nsomething other than yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:57.34,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,It's important both to protect that \Nsomething, as well as for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:02.24,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and I'll always love Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.55,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:11.03,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I wish it were that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.55,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You're so obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.37,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.37,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.64,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.04,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,We just moved here recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.45,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.39,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,It's remote, but it's nice here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:38.63,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to come see my \Ngarden, if you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.82,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,The queens will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.61,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're a Sleigh Beggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.73,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.57,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of me, and I'll eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.10,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,A Leannán Sídhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:56.20,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,She's a vampire that grants a man \Ntalent in exchange for his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.52,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, you're just a doggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.67,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your kind interested in younger men?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.41,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Suck that man's blood,\Nand he'll die in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:08.15,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're Thorn's bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.01,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.25,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.74,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two like to come in for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.95,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Go get some rest, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:21.27,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale from your lack of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.74,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know if I find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.51,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.28,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Mess with her, and I'll \Nrip you apart, vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:38.44,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I live alone here, so I've been longing for someone to have some tea with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.42,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Joel Garland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.68,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.86,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Chise Hatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.29,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,That's an amazing book collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:48.42,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I like books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.09,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I write my own, occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.85,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:57.36,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I have a short story, actually. \NCould I ask you to read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:01.23,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.62,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.52,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.96,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,It might take a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.58,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.84,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,It was a love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.61,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,A simple story about two people \Nwho meet in a rose garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.90,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,But there was something nostalgic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.81,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it a nice story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:55.51,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but it didn't seem like you \Nwere giving him the talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.57,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you haunting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.62,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking his blood, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:10.47,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like our eyes met that \Nday, in the rose garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.07,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he's my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.63,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,He's old, and a skinny slob to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:26.15,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have anything he's devoting \Nhis life to or anything, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.42,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't take his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.97,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't give him what I otherwise could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.67,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:42.80,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, since you're a human, \Nyou understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.81,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't believe I dozed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.13,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I've been really sleepy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:56.92,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Was that story about the roses here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.93,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:04.68,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,I once saw someone very beautiful \Nhere, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:08.94,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been a daydream, \Nbut it must have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.19,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Joel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.49,Default,Fan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.68,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like our eyes met again just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.53,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Was it because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.51,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in lo—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.81,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the answer I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.12,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,We love by consuming and giving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:50.53,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.77,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,Come give him a visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.84,Default,Service,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.60,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:13.30,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a word that I deserve to say \Nwhen all I can think about is myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:14.38,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:15.74,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.88,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.62,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the forests north of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:44.83,Default,Dorg,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.21,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.80,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to come \Ninto the forest at dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.77,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,I left you a note saying \NI'd be home by night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:13.23,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to tell \Nme anything, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:19.47,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Why this is happening, what \Nkind of creature you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.72,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,You always avoid me when I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.98,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,You're always quick to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.63,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,You accepted what I said \Nwithout questioning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.42,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.63,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how selfish I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:42.59,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,it's not like I'm so disinterested in you \Nthat I can bear not knowing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.88,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you make such a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.87,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Was I making a weird face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.18,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've never seen you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.11,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Were you looking for me the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.84,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,I left you a note and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.29,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:58.79,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:20:59.86,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:04.13,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me to just take that note and \Nleave you, with the way things were going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:09.96,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I may accept everything you say,\Nbut if you vanish on me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.87,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you resting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.76,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,My body's out of balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.29,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,I was here adjusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.20,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Half of what he says is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:24.77,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.58,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mind him trying to \Ngloss things over before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.43,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so scared now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:39.02,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,As for any other questions you may have\Nabout me, could you give me a little time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.77,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,I want time to gather my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.82,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.10,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.87,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.01,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Not {\i1}angry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:57.03,Default,Hikkias,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:59.07,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:00.84,Default,Gremlin,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.39,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Elias!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:06.92,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:09.81,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,Echos' familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:15.32,Default,Gremlin,0000,0000,0000,,"From Lindenbaum to Thorn."\NI have a message from Lindel-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:18.52,Default,Gremlin,0000,0000,0000,,"I have business with the child\Nyou foster. Come quickly..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.40,Default,Gremlin,0000,0000,0000,,"To the land of dragons."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:58.74,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,The girl visits the land of \Ndragons for a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:03.39,Default,Chissu,0000,0000,0000,,There, she learns of a side to the mage\N that she'd never known before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:08.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It came as certain as the night.
